        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Lastly at 3rd level, you gain the following Channel the Force option.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<h4><strong>DISARMING SLASH</strong></h4>\n<p>When you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack, you can expend a use of your Channel the Force (no action required) to attempt to disarm the target, forcing it to drop one item of your choice that it&rsquo;s holding. The creature must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save, it drops the object you choose. If you are within 5 feet of the target, and you have a free hand, you can catch the item. Otherwise, the object lands at its feet.</p>\n</blockquote>",
